<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
</head>

<body style="margin: 0;background: whitesmoke;">


    <div style=" font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; padding-bottom: 1rem; padding-top: 1rem;">
        <div
            style="width: 90%; max-width: 32rem;margin: 0 auto;text-align: center; padding: 2rem 1rem; background: white; border-top: 5px solid #f35327;">
            <h1 style="font-size: 1rem; text-transform: capitalize;">Hi {{username}},</h1>
            <div style="font-weight: light;text-align: center;">Congratulations on reaching your goal target, We're glad you achieved this through dedication and determination, Be sure to check your account balance as it'll reflect your recently withdrawn savings. We're here to help you save more!
            </div>
            <h2 style="font-size: 1.2rem;">Goal Savings Details</h2>
            <div style="background-color: whitesmoke;padding: 0.5rem;">
                <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: row; justify-content: space-between;padding: 0.5rem;">
                    <div style="text-align: left;">Goal Savings Name</div>
                    <div style="width: fit-content; margin-left: auto; text-transform: capitalize;">{{goalname}}</div>
                </div>
                <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: row; justify-content: space-between;padding: 0.5rem;">
                    <div style="text-align: left;">Goal Target</div>
                    <div style="width: fit-content; margin-left: auto;">{{goaltarget}}</div>
                </div>
                <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: row; justify-content: space-between;padding: 0.5rem;">
                    <div style="text-align: left;">Current amount saved</div>
                    <div style="width: fit-content; margin-left: auto;">{{goalcurrent}}</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div style="padding: 1rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid lightgrey;margin-bottom: 1rem;">{{date}}</div>
            <div>
                If you need help or support, kindly contact Santtandder Bank  support  at support@santtandderbank.com or simply reply to this email.</div>
        </div>

    </div>
</body>

</html>